This paper is primarily focused on video object segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised learning methods, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with the analysis of data and the development of algorithms, which could fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
